Mystic Arms :
-------------
North of the underground entrance of Hythloth, tis there northward across
cavernous peaks from the dungeon admist the boiling lava, that the mystic
arms are said to lie.  Only the mystic arms work near great evil.

Amulet Info:
------------
With only this (amulet) can the find thy path in a place of unholy
Darkness, which I have for-seen shall block thy way.  Tis beyond such a
place that through must search, if thou art to mend the injustice wrought
upon the world by Lord Blackthorn and his Spectres.

