Text You get at the Codex, after you free all the shrines
---------------------------------------------------------

Beyond Shames Egress is the Centre of the UnderWorld.  There is a place of
Darkness!  Beyond this Darkness lies the gate to the core of the worlds.
When thou art ready thou must call forth "VERAMOCOR" to unlock the Gate and
venture past the ethereal wards and stealers of souls.  That which the
world hath lost awaits thy coming!

